  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个完整的认证流程图，涉及Web客户端、Keycloak授权服务器和Synapse服务器。Web客户端是公开的，Synapse作为后端服务需要机密客户端凭证。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Web Client (Public)",
        "Keycloak",
        "Synapse Server",
        "client_id",
        "client_secret"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，我先确认一下结构：三个参与者横向排列，Web Client在左，Keycloak居中，Synapse在右。初始阶段需要标注注册流程对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Web Client (Public)",
        "Keycloak",
        "Synapse Server",
        "Initial Setup"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，Synapse和Web Client都要先向Keycloak注册，但方式不同——Synapse用client_id加client_secret，Web Client只用client_id，标记为public。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Synapse Server",
        "Keycloak",
        "Web Client (Public)",
        "client_id",
        "client_secret",
        "public"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，注册部分画好了。接下来是认证流程，我理解为标准的授权码模式：Web Client请求授权码，Keycloak重定向返回，然后交换token？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Web Client (Public)",
        "Keycloak",
        "Authorization Code Request",
        "Redirect with Auth Code",
        "Token Request",
        "Access & Refresh Tokens"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，第三步注意要标注code + client_id。然后Synapse作为服务端的认证是独立的，用client_credentials流程获取token。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Synapse Server",
        "Keycloak",
        "Token Request",
        "client_credentials",
        "Access Token"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
