      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "服务端认证部分已完成。现在画API通信：Web Client带着Access Token请求Synapse，Synapse需要向Keycloak做token introspection验证？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Web Client (Public)",
